  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that a three-month aerobic exercise training program will
      positively affect the lipid profile, insulin sensitivity , cytokine profile, the
      cardiovascular parameters and muscle strength in SLE patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
