  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Lipid profile - Plasma levels of total cholesterol (mg/dl), VLDL-chol (mg/dl) HDL-chol (mg/dl), LDL-chol (mg/dl), triglycerides (mg/dl), Apolipoprotein AI and AII (mg/dl) and Apolipoprotein B (mg/dl)</measure>
